Cytotoxicity of the methanol extracts and compounds of Brucea antidysenterica 
(Simaroubaceae) towards multifactorial drug-resistant human cancer cell lines.

Youmbi LM(1)(2), Makong YSD(3), Mbaveng AT(1)(4), Tankeo SB(1)(4), Fotso GW(5), 
Ndjakou BL(6), Wansi JD(3), Beng VP(2), Sewald N(7), Ngadjui BT(5), Efferth 
